description: Welcome to The Muse! This completely renovated historic factory building combines its rustic roots with luxurious, high-end updates for a stunning modern look. Step inside and be greeted by soaring vaulted ceilings, exposed brick, and breathtaking city views. The unit features a contemporary kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a reverse osmosis water purification system, and convenient in-unit laundry. Every detail has been carefully designed to blend the charm of the past with the convenience of modern living. Recently replaced water heater (July 2025). Located just minutes from South Station, the Financial District, the Waterfront, and the lively neighborhoods of South Boston and South End, this home offers unmatched access to all the city has to offer. Don't miss your opportunity to own a piece of Boston's rich history. This exceptional property won't last long!
